    "After absorbing the natural calm of the Jardim Botânico, we re-enter our limousine and journey to a place that pulses with human creativity: the Escadaria Selarón. As we approach the bohemian neighborhood of Lapa, our guide points towards the vivid staircase that spills down the street like a river of color." /
