    "Leaving the sacred grounds of the Fortaleza de São João, we move from the contemplative military history to the artistic allure of the Teatro Municipal. As the limousine arrives at the theater, we are immediately struck by the lavishness of its exterior, a sign to Brazil's vibrant cultural life." /
