    "After the curtain call at the lavish Teatro Municipal, our sensory journey takes us to the quiet embrace of nature at Lagoa Rodrigo de Freitas. The limousine coasts to a stop at the edge of this picturesque lagoon, an oasis of calm in the midst of Rio's vibrant energy." /
